Note on book content
--------------------

The MIT License above covers the **source code** of this site only:
Hugo templates, CSS, JavaScript, build scripts, and configuration.

The **book content** included in `content/` and the downloadable PDFs in
`static/downloads/` — most notably *Carrom Techniques and Skills* by
Arun Deshpande — remain the intellectual property of their respective
authors:

  © Arun Deshpande — *Carrom Techniques and Skills* and all original
  coaching material on this site. All rights reserved.

The *Official Carrom Rules & Regulations* chapter content is summarised
from publicly-available sources (International Carrom Federation
laws and wikiHow). See `data/books.yaml` for source attribution.

If you wish to reproduce, translate, or redistribute Arun Deshpande's
coaching book in any form, please contact him through the channels
listed on the site.
